<p>
<b>IV - THE SITUATION OF CHILDREN IN COUNTRIES OF THE CONVENIO</b><p>
<p>
<p>
<b>The Condition of Children</b><p>
<p>
	Table 3 provides an overview of several commonly-used indicators of the
condition of children in countries of the Convenio Andres Bello.  <p>
<p>
<p>
