</pre>
<p>
In terms of coverage, while one issue is the percentage of the age cohort that
is being served, another important question to ask is, what is the distribution
of child care centres throughout the country?  In Table 4 is the distribution
of preschool centres by State and in Table 5 is the number of registered child
care centres by State.  In the tables, the states have been listed in terms of
the mean monthly household income, with the state having the highest mean
household income being listed first.<p>
