<p>
	Within this time period there will be a Task Force Meeting<p>
<p>
October - 1st 2 weeks - Data analysis<p>
	     3rd week - writing<p>
	     4th week - in mail to all attending meeting in November<p>
				(report sent to JLE)<p>
<p>
November 16-17 - Second Workshop - Final review<p>
<p>
