<p>
<p>
<p>
<center>Tables</center><p>
<pre>
Table 1  	ECD Programmes for Children 3-6 years of age by Sponsor, 1991	   <p>
Table 2  	Number of Day Care and Pre-school Centres Serving Children 0-6, 
		by Region and Sponsor, 1992					 	 
<p>
Table 3		Number of Day Care and Pre-school Centres Serving Children 0-6, 
		by Region and Type of Provision, 1992					 
<p>
