<p>
<center><b>NEPAL: FROM ENTRY POINT TO CONSOLIDATION</b> <p>
<p>
<p>
<b>AN ASSESSMENT OF EARLY CHILDHOOD PROVISION IN NEPAL</b><p>
<b>WITH RECOMMENDATIONS FOR</b><p>
<b>UNICEF'S INVOLVEMENT </b><p>

<p>
<b>Report of a Consultancy conducted</b><p>
<b></b><p>
<b>by</b><p>
<b></b><p>
<b>Judith L. Evans</b><p>
<b></b><p>
<b>September 1992</b><p>
</center>
<p>
<p>
<p>
 <p>
