Attached please find a copy of my consultancy report on the development of
instruments to assess preschool sector activities in Viet Nam.<p>
<p>
I would like to express my appreciation to UNICEF/Socialist Republic of Vietnam
for their support of this consultancy.  It is with much respect and admiration
that I complement the UNICEF Programme Officers, the Ministry of Education's
Preschool Sector Steering Committee, Mrs. Mai Chi and all the members of the
working group for their participation in an intellectually challenging and
productive working session. I wish them much success in their analysis of the
strengths and weakness of the preschool sector activities and look forward to
the insights provided by through their report. <p>
<p>
If needed, I would be honored to provide additional technical assistance as
requested. <p>
<p>
