	Easy	           1		   2		   3
<p>
	Flexible	   1		   2		   3
<p>
	Age
	Appropriate	   1		   2		   3<p>
<p>
</pre>
23. 	How adequate are your teacher's aids/materials?<p>
<pre>
			   1		   2		   3<p>
<p>
</pre>
