<H2>
Previously in Random Access Humor 96
</H2>
<P>
Here is the material that previously appeared on the RAH96 main menu.
A few seasonal or topical items may be cycled back to the main menu
when appropriate. 
</P>
<P>
For more published works by your favorite RAH authors, check their
<A HREF="rstaff.html">personal home pages</A>.
</P>
<P>
