<H3>  
<A NAME="Comment">The Commentaries</A>
</H3>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/brahbul.gif">
<A HREF="harrumph.html">Random Insanity Online - The Next Generation</A><BR>
Dave's initial editorial for RAH96. (1996)
</P>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/brahbul.gif">
<A HREF="olcountd.html">Olympic Countdown</A><BR>
Dave comments on pre-Olympic hysteria. Includes 200K of graphics. (1996)
</P>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/brahbul.gif">
<A HREF="declr220.html">The Declaration at 220: Those Old Words Still Ring 
True</A><BR>
Dave salutes the U.S. Declaration of Independence and its far-sighted,
politically incorrect authors. (1996)
</P>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/brahbul.gif">
<A HREF="puritan.html">Puritanical Gardens</A><BR>
Dave reflects on how the puritans have screwed up America. (1996)
</P>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/brahbul.gif">
<A HREF="spree.html">The Spree Is Over</A><BR>
Dave pre-presidential election editorial. (1996)
</P>
<H3>
<A NAME="Dialogue">The Dialogues</A>
</H3>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/brahbul.gif">
<A HREF="25kstill.html">A 25000 Year Still Life</A><BR>
Greg proves once again that the more things change, the more they
stay the same. This story was featured in the RAH96 review that 
appeared in the December 1996 issue of <i>Yahoo Internet Life</i>. (1996)
</P>
<H3>
<A NAME="Parodies">The Parodies</A>
</H3>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/brahbul.gif">
<A HREF="wholnewt.html">Song Parody: A Whole Newt World</A><BR>
Dave's political parody based on the wonderful love song "A Whole
New World" from the Disney classic <i>Aladdin</i>. (1996)
</P>
<H3>
<A NAME="Reviews">RAH96 Humor Reviews</A>
</H3>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/brahbul.gif">
<A HREF="dilzone.html">The Dilbert Zone</A><BR>
A review of the web site supporting the best comic strip of the 1990s. (1996)
</P>
<H3>
<A NAME="Features">Features</A>
</H3>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/brahbul.gif">
<A HREF="taglines.html">Taglines - July 1996</A><BR>
Features taglines and music from the British science fiction 
situation comedy "Red Dwarf." (1996)
</P>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/brahbul.gif">
<A HREF="oddparty.html">Odd Parity - July 1996</A><BR>
Graduation congrats to the class of 1996. Virtual reality.
</P>
