<A HREF="http://www.digits.com/">Web-Counter</A>.<BR>
In case you die before the page count server responds to your request, 
make provisions in your will so the executor of your estate terminates the 
PPP connection. If not, those hourly charges may eat up your entire legacy 
before the lawyers even get started picking over the remains.
</P>
<P>
This site is tuned for 
<A HREF="http://home.netscape.com/comprod/mirror/"><IMG SRC="/grph/nsnow20.gif" alt="Netscape Navigator V2.0."></A><BR>
We don't use many Netscape-specific HTML codes, unless we're deliberately
looking to <BLINK>annoy</BLINK> our readers. In any event you will experience 
greater enjoyment (and less confusion) at this site if your browser supports 
tables and forms.
</P>
<P>
Dave's Homepage has a MIDI soundtrack which is best heard with
<A HREF="http://www.liveupdate.com/crescendo.html">
<IMG SRC="/grph/cresbut1.gif" alt="Crescendo by Liveupdate."></A><BR>
Although the Windows Media Player should also serve the purpose.<BR>
Use of a wavetable sound card is strongly recommended.
</P>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/notes.gif" ALT=""><BR>
<BGSOUND SRC="/midi/rootbeer.mid">
<EMBED SRC="/midi/rootbeer.mid" WIDTH=200 HEIGHT=55><BR>
