<H2>
RAH96: Odd Parity
</H2>
<P>
Miscellaneous insanity from both the online and "real" worlds.
</P>
<H3>
Congratulations Class of 1996!
</H3>
<P>
The graduate with a Science degree asks, "Why does it work?"
</P>
<P>
The graduate with an Engineering degree asks, "How does it work?"
</P>
<P>
The graduate with an Accounting degree asks, "How much will it cost?"
</P>
<P>
The graduate with a Liberal Arts degree asks, "Do you want mustard with that?"
</P>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/rah96bar.gif" ALT="______________________________">
</P>
<H3>
The Virtual Reality Test
</H3>
<P>
If you can see it,<BR>
And you can touch it,<BR>
It's real.
</P>
<P>
If you can touch it,<BR>
But you can't see it,<BR>
It's transparent.
</P>
<P>
If you can see it,<BR>
But you can't touch it,<BR>
It's virtual.
</P>
<P>
If you can't see it,<BR>
And you can't touch it,<BR>
It's gone!
</P>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/rah96bar.gif" ALT="______________________________">
