<H2>
Selected Works Written by Dave Bealer
</H2>
<P>
Here are a few choice (read: least barf-inducing) items written
by Dave Bealer over the years:
</P>
<H3>
The Commentaries
</H3>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/davewbul.gif">
<A HREF="dreamon.html">The Dream Is On Life Support</A><BR>
Dave's serious, heartfelt commentary on the failure of the space program
to fulfill its potential. (1994)
</P>
<H3>
The Reviews
</H3>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/davewbul.gif">
<A HREF="ifyrfat.html">Book Review: <I>If You're Fat, It's Not Your
Fault</I></A><BR>
Dave reviews a book which describes the medical weight loss plan that
has changed his life. Yes, this is for real. No, Dave has no financial
interest in this program. (1996)
</P>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/davewbul.gif">
<A HREF="atrouble.html">Book Review: <I>All The Trouble In The World</I></A>
<BR>
Dave reviews the 1995 best seller by P.J. O'Rourke which debunks many of the
most popular myths about famine, overpopulation, ethnic hatred, and poverty.
</P>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/davewbul.gif">
<A HREF="dracula.html">Movie Review: <I>Dracula - Dead And Loving It</I></A>
<BR>
Dave reviews the 1995 Mel Brooks comedy.
</P>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/davewbul.gif">
<A HREF="kanstyx.html">Music Review: Kansas/Styx Summer Tour 1996</A><BR>
Dave's review of the Kansas/Styx concert in Columbia, MD. on 6/2/96.
Includes the concert schedule for the remainder of the Summer Tour:
June-August 1996.
</P>
<H3>
Grab Bag
</H3>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/davewbul.gif">
<A HREF="sillypar.html">Silly Parties</A><BR>
Strange party invitations and theme parties/picnics. (1995)
</P>
<P>
For many more items written by Dave over the years, see the
<A HREF="/rah96/bestrah.html">Best of RAH</A> page on the RAH96 site.
</P>
