<BODY BGCOLOR=#091157 TEXT=#FFFFFF LINK=#FFFF00 VLINK=FF00FF>
<CENTER>
<H2>
Dave's Photo Gallery
</H2>
<P>
Here are a few pictures of Dave and his cats.
<IMG SRC="http://rah96.com/cgi-bin/Count.exe?df=davephtg.dat|sh=0" ALT="">
</P>
<H3>
Welcome
</H3>
</CENTER>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/davesgn1.gif" align="left" width="320" height="240">
Dave cornered in the foyer of his home. Note the friendly, welcoming
signs that he has posted around the place.
<BR><BR><BR>
<BR><BR><BR>
<BR><BR><BR>
<BR><BR><BR>
</P>
<CENTER>
<H3>
Rascal
</H3>
</CENTER>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/daverasc.gif" align="right" width="320" height="240">
<BR><BR><BR>
Dave holds Rascal, a 12 year old male orange and white tabby cat.
Dave adopted Rascal in 1991, soon after moving into his current home.
Rascal is a real slut for attention and loves to be held. Rascal enjoys
food almost as much as Dave does. They're both getting grumpier in 
their old age, as well.
<BR><BR><BR>
</P>
<CENTER>
<H3>
Velvet
</H3>
</CENTER>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/davelvt1.gif" align="left" width="320" height="240">
Dave holds Velvet, a four year old female black tabby cat. Velvet has
very fine red tabby markings visible in her fur, although they'd never
show up in any picture resolution available online.  She also has a 
small white diamond on her throat. Velvet was adopted as a kitten in
late 1991 to keep Rascal company while Dave is at work. Velvet was found 
abandoned as a very young kitten, and she may never recover fully from 
that ordeal. Greg has affectionately nicknamed her "The Demon from Hell" 
because of her sudden, insanely violent tendencies.
</P>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/grph/davelvt2.gif" align="right" width="320" height="240">
Dave holds Velvet in one of her rare calmer moments. This moment lasted
several nanoseconds before Velvet tired of it and started violently
scrambling to get away. Velvet can be very affectionate when <i>she</i>
is ready. In fact, she curled up at Dave's feet purring while he grabbed
these frames from the videotape. 
<BR><BR><BR>
<BR><BR><BR>
</P>
