HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 01 Jan 1997 08:49:50 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.5
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 5623
Last-modified: Sun, 07 Jul 1996 05:05:36 GMT
